rComments: I had him for Psychology of Death and Dying, his course was very fun and did not feel dark and depressing as the course title says! I do recommend this prof, he is straight to the point and the lectures go by very quickly as he ends them early. Just beware of the paper as it was tough to work on other than that amazing course and prof!!
Great prof! Lectures were interesting content that was easy to follow. Midterm and final were both super fair - attend the lectures and you will do well. Such a cutie too. 10/10 recommend!
